## Shipping commitment

The shape described here plus the specific type and method names locked
in the src CL of the round introducing this crate. Follow-up design
rounds may extend the crate (for example to add explicit unload,
telemetry, or additional platform targets) but must preserve the v1
contract unless explicit deprecation is scheduled.
